title: Check for hardware sensors on OpenBSD devices
agents: snmp, openbsd
catalog: os/misc
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk

description:
 This check monitors the state of {{temperature sensors}} of a hardware
 system running OpenBSD if this data is provided by SNMP.  These Services
 are using the standard values for warn/crit and are configurable like other
 checks of the same type.

item:
 The item is the description of the sensor.

inventory:
 A Service is created for each sensor item if there is a valid output.
